  "commit_message": "internal: reuse verified cy-prompt/Studio bundle cache to avoid publish failures (#33979)\n\n* fix: reuse verified cy-prompt/Studio bundle cache to avoid publish failures\n\nSince 15.15.0, every `cypress run` re-downloaded the cy-prompt/Studio bundle\nand re-published it over the already-populated cache dir (the in-memory\nhashLoadingMap only dedupes within a single process). The per-file rename onto\na destination held open by a sibling process (the loaded bundle) or scanned by\nAV failed with EPERM/EA",
